Description: New input method framework using dbus
 IBus is an Intelligent Input Bus. It is a new input framework for Linux
 OS. It provides full featured and user friendly input method user interface.
 It also may help developers to develop input method easily.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static libraries which is
 needed for developing the IBus applications.

Package: ibus-gtk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: New input method framework using dbus (GTK+2 support)
 IBus is an Intelligent Input Bus. It is a new input framework for Linux
 OS. It provides full featured and user friendly input method user interface.
 It also may help developers to develop input method easily.
 .
 ibus-gtk is the GTK+2 client of ibus, it provide a gtk-immodule for ibus.
 
